e\" Grusinsky\n| Also producer \n|- \n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=2| 2008\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Happening (2008 film)|The Happening]]''\n| Elliot Moore\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Max Payne (film)|Max Payne]]''\n| [[Max Payne (character)|Max Payne]]\n|  \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2009\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Lovely Bones (film)|The Lovely Bones]]''\n| Jack Salmon\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=3| 2010\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Date Night]]''\n| Holbrooke Grant\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Other Guys]]''\n| Detective Terry Hoitz\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Fighter]]''\n| [[Micky Ward]]\n| Also producer\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=2| 2012\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Contraband (2012 film)|Contraband]]''\n| Chris Farraday\n| Also producer \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[Ted (film)|Ted]]''\n| John Bennett\n| \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=4| 2013\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[Broken City]]''\n| Billy Taggart\n| Also producer\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[Pain & Gain]]''\n| Daniel Lugo\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[2 Guns]]''\n| Michael \"Stig\" Stigman\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[Lone Survivor]]''\n| [[Marcus Luttrell]]\n| Also producer\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=2| 2014\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[Transformers: Age of Extinction]]''\n| Cade Yeager\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[The Gambler (2014 film)|The Gambler]]''\n| Jim Bennett\n| Also producer \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=4| 2015\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Mojave (film)|Mojave]]''\n| Norman\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[Entourage (film)|Entourage]]''\n| Himself\n| Also producer\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[Ted 2]]''\n| John Bennett\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Daddy's Home (film)|Daddy's Home]]''\n| Dusty Mayron\n| \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=2| 2016\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Deepwater Horizon (film)|Deepwater Horizon]]''\n| Mike Williams\n| Also producer \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Patriots Day 