stitute (1993 film)|The Substitute]]''\n| Ryan Westerberg\n| [[Television film]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Ben Stiller Show]]''\n| rowspan=\"6\" | Himself\n| Episode: \"A Few Good Scouts\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Out All Night (TV series)|Out All Night]]''\n| Episode: \"Under My Thumb\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2004<br />2008<br />2009<br />2010\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Entourage (U.S. TV series)|Entourage]]''\n| {{ubl|\"Pilot\"|\"Unlike a Virgin\" (5.2)|\"Fore\" (6.5)|\"Tequila and Coke\" (7.7)}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2008\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Saturday Night Live]]''\n| Episode: \"Josh Brolin/Adele\" (4.5)\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2014\u20132019\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Wahlburgers (TV series)|Wahlburgers]]''\n| 36 episodes\n|-\n|2020\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Ant & Dec's Saturday Night Takeaway]]''\n|1 episode; special guest\n|}\n\n=== Fitness documentary ===\n* ''Form... Focus... Fitness, the Marky Mark Workout'' (1993)<ref>{{Citation|last=Kalvert|first=Scott|title=Form... Focus... Fitness, the Marky Mark Workout|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0264844/|others=Johnny Alves, Rebecca Budig, Connie Chambers|accessdate=December 19, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418160635/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0264844/|archive-date=April 18, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n===Producer===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2004\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Juvies'' \n| Executive producer\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2004\u20132011\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Entourage (U.S. TV series)|Entourage]]''\n| Executive producer\n| \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2007\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[We Own the Night (film)|We Own the Night]]''\n| Producer\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2008\u20132010\n! scope=\"row\" |  ''[[In Treatment (U.