l Charts|GER]]<br><ref name=\"lescharts\"/>\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[Swiss Music Charts|SWI]]<br><ref name=\"lescharts\"/>\n! style=\"width:33px;\"| [[Eurochart Hot 100|EUR]]<ref name=\"British Hit Singles & Albums\" />\n|-\n| 1995\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''[[The Remix Album (Prince Ital Joe album)|The Remix Album]]''\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|\n|}\n\n===Singles===\n====Marky Mark and the Funky Bunch====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Single\n! colspan=\"10\"| Peak chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| [[Music recording sales certification|Certifications]]<br><small>([[List of best selling music artists|sales threshold]])</small>\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[Billboard Hot 100|US]]<br><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/309618/marky-mark/chart?f=379|title=Billboard > Artists / Marky Mark > Chart History > The Hot 100|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=February 23, 2017|date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223225525/http://www.billboard.com/artist/309618/marky-mark/chart?f=379|archive-date=February 23, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br><ref name=aus/>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[\u00d63 Austria Top 40|AUT]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.austriancharts.at/search.asp?search=marky+mark&cat=s|title=austriancharts.at - Austria Top 40|publisher=austriancharts.at|accessdate=July 9, 2010|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68sEKL7Ki?url=http://www.austriancharts.at/search.asp?search=marky+mark|archive-date=July 3, 2012|url-status=live}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[RPM (magazine)|CAN]]<br><ref name=\"Peak\">*For Good Vibrations: [http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?&file_num=nlc008388.1660&type=1&interval=20&PHPSESSID=j86d3uqb5jajlou8j8ag1r4lv4 Peak] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309060649/http://www.colle